@node KillMarked.zprx
@toc Skripten_A-Z

    $VER: KillMarked.zprx 1.1 (04.12.94) by Ralph Seichter
    ARexx script for Zodiac's Point 3.9.

    This script adds the flags "old" and "deleted" to the currently
    marked messages and jumps down to the next new message. I suggest
    you to bind this script to an F-Key, e.g. by adding

        F1:SYS:Rexxc/RX ZP:Rexx/KillMarked.zprx %s

    to your "fkeys.zp" file. You cann pass an options after the
    port name, i.e. "KillMarked.zprx ZPoint FORCE LATER".

